---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Koios · Privacy Notice for the Parkiwatch questionnaire"
  description="How Koios Care collects, uses and protects the personal data you provide through the Parkiwatch pilot interest questionnaire."
>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Privacy</span>
      <h1 style="margin-top:18px">Privacy Notice for the <em>questionnaire</em>.</h1>
    </div>
    <p class="lead" style="margin-top:22px">How Koios Care collects, uses and protects the personal data you provide when you express interest in the PARKIWATCH pilot.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DOCUMENT -->
<section style="padding-top:calc(20px*var(--density))">
  <div class="wrap">
    <article class="doc-prose reveal">

      <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
      <p>Koios Care BV, Filip Williotstraat 9, 2600, Antwerpen, Belgium, company number BE 0786.830.148 (&lsquo;Koios Care&rsquo;, &lsquo;we&rsquo;), is the controller of the personal data collected through this questionnaire.</p>
      <p>Data Protection Officer: Vasileios Papapanagiotou, reachable at <a href="mailto:vasileios@koios.care">vasileios@koios.care</a>.</p>

      <h2>2. What we collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>your name and email address;</li>
        <li>mobile number &mdash; optional field, only if you want to be contacted by phone;</li>
        <li>city <strong>or</strong> postal code &mdash; choose one, not both;</li>
        <li>the fact that you have expressed interest in a pilot for people living with Parkinson&rsquo;s disease.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Because of the context of this questionnaire, all of the above is treated as health data (special category data, Art. 9 GDPR).</p>

      <h2>3. Why, and on what legal basis</h2>
      <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> to assess your interest and eligibility and to contact you about possible participation in the PARKIWATCH pilot programme. Nothing else &mdash; we do not use this data for marketing, and we do not sell or share it for third-party purposes.</p>
      <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> your explicit consent (Art. 6(1)(a) and Art. 9(2)(a) GDPR), given via the checkbox on the form. You can withdraw it at any time via <a href="mailto:info@koios.care">info@koios.care</a>; withdrawal does not affect processing that happened before withdrawal.</p>

      <h2>4. Who sees your data</h2>
      <p>Only the Koios Care team involved in recruitment. Our form/survey tool provider processes the data on our behalf as a processor under a data processing agreement: Google Ireland Ltd acts as our processor under the Google Workspace Data Processing Addendum; any transfer to the United States is covered by Google LLC&rsquo;s certification under the EU&ndash;US Data Privacy Framework.</p>

      <h2>5. How long we keep it</h2>
      <p>If you do not enrol in the pilot, we delete your questionnaire data within 6 months of submission. If you do enrol, your data is transferred into the pilot documentation and the pilot-specific privacy notice and consent will apply from that point.</p>

      <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access your data, to have it corrected or deleted, to restrict processing, to data portability, and to withdraw your consent at any time. To exercise any of these, email <a href="mailto:info@koios.care">info@koios.care</a>. You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the Belgian Data Protection Authority (Gegevensbeschermingsautoriteit / Autorit&eacute; de protection des donn&eacute;es, <a href="https://www.dataprotectionauthority.be" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.dataprotectionauthority.be</a>) or with the supervisory authority of your own country.</p>

      <h2>7. Other things you should know</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Providing your data is entirely voluntary; the only consequence of not providing it is that we cannot contact you about the pilot.</li>
        <li>We do not use your data for automated decision-making or profiling.</li>
        <li>Your data is stored within the EU/EEA.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="doc-foot">
        <p>This Privacy Notice may be updated periodically. Please check back for any changes.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
